{
  "text": "where µ ∈ (0, 4] and x 0 is control parameter and initial value of map, respectively. This map has two main drawbacks: firstly, Its chaotic range is limited [3.57, 4] , and secondly, µ beyond the range cannot generate chaotic behaviors [CITATION_1] .",
